All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    This class represents an admin that can access the MySTARS Application An admin class inherits from a User class
    AdminManager
    This class is responsible for handing the logic to fulfill the functions of admin UI
    AdminUI
    This class is responsible for handing the user interactions between the admin and the application to perform the necessary admin tasks
    Course
    Represents a Course which a Student can take
    CourseManager
    CourseManager handles the input and ouput of data into the different entity courses.
    dataGeneration
    Create the data required for the application
    fileManager
    This class is in charge of saving and loading student, admin and courses data files.
    Index
    Index object containing the details of a course such as the lessons and size.
    Lesson
    Lesson object containing the details of a Lecture/Tutorial/Lab.
    LoginController
    This class is responsible for handing the logic to fulfill the login of the users.
    MailManager
    This Control Class is responsible of handling the Email Notification to students in the system
    mainApp
    This class serves as the the entry point of the program.
    Student
    Represents a student user that can access the MySTARS Application A student class inherit from a User class
    StudentManager
    Manages the functionalities avaliable to a student
    StudentUI
    UI for the user to manage the courses in the STARS system.
    User
    Represents a user that can access the STARS Application A user can be either an admin or student in the application
